\section{Miscellaneous} 
\label{sec:misc}



Note that the value returned by \yacas\ can be of different types:
@ 
<<print=T>>=
yacas(expression(Factor(x^2-1)),retclass='unquote')
yacas(expression(Factor(x^2-1)),retclass='character')
@ %def 


